name: Years Ago
description:
This was my own first trip to the USA. 
First trip with my mask and pure dreams.
I had a plan to film a short documentary film but all my equipment broke down so I filmed and edited this video on my phone.
I didn't have any friends in the USA  - no work - no money - no place to live. Bad moments in my life helped me find interesting stories.
So I found a lot of new friends and they inspired me so much. 
My equipment was broken but not my mask and never my imagination. Bunny was always on my back for 2 years.

Music by: Zhan Davids
